name: yuki
description: Yuki the Cat: Snow, luck, and unstoppable energy in the Toshi ecosystem. $YUKI is a character with lore, not just a meme. Fortune is coming. yuki was created by a group of 3 friends from the toshi community over the last year. we strive to bring white cat content in the shape of memes art and good vibe messages. yuki is more then just a meme.
